Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought my project was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did I make a mistake? What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, I'm gonna look at your script.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me as much as you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! What, you're going on a date again or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to toss it into the game program and put it into a game format!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But the script's not finished at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, you can't finish it before the Comic Stall anyway, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for this time, I'll just make it a sample and code in only the best parts of the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A sample?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't necessarily promise that I'd put out a finished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If the people in my class say anything, I'll tell them the truth:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"The reason is that Sato fell behind on his script."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty much because you're all gaga over a girl that things turn out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd been seriously working, by now we'd have...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sounds sort of like someone else I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:05.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCFCECC&\pos(1078.651,189.076)\fad(1985,0)}Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we've reached a stopping point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's at least have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're busy at work, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Things will settle down by the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have to cancel our long-awaited trip or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise I made to you, Hitomi, and that's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it me that's important? Or is it the promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really like to walk you up to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going back to the office to keep working, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hana-Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I fought with my boyfriend again today, at the grungy yakitori place we always go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said, "What if I got a real job?" He flipped out and got violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He hit me all over; I'm still sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this kind of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of taking part in the offline meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why, when I think of a troubled person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato comes to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you read it, Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing delicate work here, so don't bother me with pointless stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He made so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these really gonna sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kashiwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At our recent meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you said if we have any proposals for how to serve citizens, you would actively accept them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so I organized my ideas into a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to take things this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If we actually started these sorts of services, think what it would cost in time and personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think it would put a strain on other duties that need to be done in the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I accounted for that in the proposal too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just armchair theory!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand the first thing about being a public servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shred this immediately, before any department heads get a look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have the time to write this stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,why not double-check the electoral register?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I double-checked it last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then triple-check it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so uppity just 'cause she's a little pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's not that forgiving a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kashiwa, don't let this kind of thing break your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on vacation starting tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I'll check the register for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a good organ-stew restaurant in Kouenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like, I could buy you dinner sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you tell me when would be good for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:53.12,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs42.352}How are you? About our trip... due to some unexpected trouble it looks like I'm not going to be able to go. Sorry... I promise I'll make it up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...unexpected trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we resolve this, there's no way I can get away from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it wasn't an important promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation is precious, so why don't you go, at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point going by myself. I'll cancel the hotel reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll make up for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still working, right? Do your best, Jogasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:09:03.05,Background,,0,0,0,,A dream and a conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a conspiracy did exist after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, why are you so slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working at less than half my pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your machine's write speed is more than double mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:38.51,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Offline meeting notice\N"The Island Nearest to Paradise" Tour\NAugust 11, 2006. 11:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare oversleep tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's only a club thing, but I want to get in by 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'll give you this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the game I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's finished; I've got this halfway kind of feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really become a game creator by making something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally escaped from being a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe it all to your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Senpai, aren't you hot in that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't relax your guard, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a huge conspiracy on a worldwide scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Promoting rapid global warming,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll increase atmospheric CO  levels and bring on an ice age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30.253\pos(647.191,692.772)}2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's their plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! I'm sure you can hear the footsteps of that winter too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's calling me this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be her, could it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai's calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai! It's me, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to the trouble of calling me and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! I'm an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, it's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, did you forget my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been shut in so long you're losing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you calling about at this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your apartment is near the Mita green belt, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you give me your address?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it. I'll be there shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's "shortly" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't be thinking of drinking at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is always sudden about things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She drove here?! How does she plan to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought both drinks and snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation is fun-fun-fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You'll wake the neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, you haven't already been drinking, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven forbid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pure and proper public servants never drive under the influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's surprisingly clean, considering you're a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd definitely spend some time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing this takes me back to our high school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It does, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I also bought some cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile. Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. We're not in high school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Senpai, who's always had a conspiracy-mania, in such a good mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her so cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I have, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was when I was in my second year of high school, at the close of the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be skipping out on things up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drink. This is from what our class didn't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:10.55,Note,,0,0,0,,Culture Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My last culture festival in high school is over now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, I throw myself headlong towards entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for the long face. I'll show my face in the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad for you playing cards all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That short-haired loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The former captain of the basketball team...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a few minutes ago, we broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was careless too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was dating that guy for two years and didn't see through to what he really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm cut off from that dirtbag, and I can concentrate on my exam studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can go to college in Tokyo without anything holding me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stroke of good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably knew what I should have done at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the end I wasn't able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That night was a crossroads in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had roused my courage and stepped forward, she and I could have become...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe I wouldn't have shut myself off like this. I could have led a respectable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This very moment may be another chance to start over in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never drunk this much before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen a lot of my miserable side from way back, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm with you, I just want to show that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right. This girl's probably going to start crying pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the time for me to gently comfort her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then with our mutual love as a support,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say goodbye to this cursed hikikomori life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai! Are you going to sleep there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I came today to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to take part in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.25,Note,,0,0,0,,Offline Meeting Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other means of escaping from the evil hands of the conspiracy that enfolds the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She was saying something about "summer vacation."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.15,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Yamazaki,\NFirst, let me apologize. I'm sorry, Yamazaki...\NSummer Comic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Gal game world that's become so stale, I'll show you a thing or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I crashed his place last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I must have passed out right where I sat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, let's hurry up and get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Something painful happened, and you want to escape, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you, wherever you want to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it's to Paradise or the far reaches of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he saw this, huh? Now he wants to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You really will?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a hikikomori anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a good opportunity to say goodbye to the cursed life I've been leading.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, if I'm with you, I'm not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that, Senpai. What are you crying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato! Where are you going? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My life as a hikikomori is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start a new life with this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF3FBEC&\pos(640,136.135)\fs60.504}Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC5E1B5&\pos(656.18,468.907)\fs60.504}Welcome to the Conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have any regrets, will you, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that gloomy group?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hana-Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They intend to end their lives today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H608DE3&\pos(640,113.445)\fs60.504}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2C69EE&\pos(640,446.219)\fs60.504}Welcome to the Offline Meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode, "Welcome to the Off Meeting!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.18,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.26,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.31,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,as I turn my back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.64,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.81,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,"Where am I supposed to go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.86,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.20,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,In the shadows of a back alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:49.33,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the hands of a clock repaint the time that has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.07,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Extended hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.44,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,puzzle pieces that don't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.74,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.79,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,reunite with something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.42,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.96,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Recover
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.22,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the last piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.35,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,and let's start walking.
